proporre un modello di descrizione e di analisi cui si dovranno attenere quanti vorranno allestire, per altri manoscritti, una trascrizione e descrizione analoga.  aThe codex Panciatichiano-Palatino 32 from the National Library in Florence is the oldest manuscript of the Novellino. It is the first Italian attempt to compile an organic collection of novellas, and it precedes the famous work by Boccaccio by several decades. This work represents a true-to-the original transcription of the entire manuscript with a detailed analysis of the abbreviations and graphic symbols.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Italian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aEdition. 4aItalien. 4aMittelalter. 4aNovellensammlung. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Italian.2bisacsh  aCollection of Novellas.  aEdition.  aItaly.  aMiddle Ages.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2011z9783110261240oZDB-23-DGA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET MEDIÄVISTIK 2010-2012z97831103011680 cprintz978311025270540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311025272940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110252729423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110252729/original  a978-3-11-030116-8  E-BOOK PAKET MEDIÄVISTIK 2010-2012c2010d2012  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2011  aZDB-23-DGGb2011  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014